      "author": {
        "id": 1152904
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-12-08T00:11:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The values of the flags are already documented in https://developer.android.com/reference/android/hardware/display/DisplayManager.\nI don\u0027t see a problem with adding an enum for the flag values and keeping the uint32 type of the flags field.",
      "parentUuid": "c111724b_825cc351",
